20 WHEREAS, more than fourteen thousand (14,000) Arkansans serve in the
21 military forces of Arkansas and the United States; and
22
23 WHEREAS, more than six thousand five hundred (6,500) children of
24 military families attend public schools in the State of Arkansas; and
25
